                <head>4. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On January 4, 1962, the United States and Vietnam issued a joint communiqué
                    outlining an expansion of economic, social, and military development programs.
                    For text of this communiqué, see American Foreign Policy: Current Documents,
                    1962, pages 1096-1098.</p>
            </div>
